parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Takata Airbag Recall Delays and Unavailability of Replacement Parts
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in replacing Takata airbags can cause serious injury or death in the event of an accident, as the faulty airbags may deploy improperly or rupture, sending shrapnel into the passenger compartment.
symptoms: Notification of recall
but parts not available for repair
no estimated date for repair
inability to schedule repair
airbag indicator randomly illuminating
dashboard cracking or splitting around airbag location.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unprofessional Business Practices and Lack of Communication
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure to provide loaner vehicles, lack of communication, and unprofessional business practices can lead to frustration, wasted time, and financial losses for vehicle owners.
symptoms: No loaner vehicle available
lack of communication
unprofessional behavior
wasted time and money
inability to schedule repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Dashboard Cracking and Airbag Deployment Concerns
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Dashboard cracking around the airbag location can cause the airbag to deploy improperly, leading to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Dashboard cracking or splitting around airbag location
concern about airbag deployment while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Fluid Leaks and Brake Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake fluid leaks and brake failure can cause loss of vehicle control, increased stopping distances, and accidents, which can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Brake fluid leaks
brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pedal travels to the floor
difficulty slowing or stopping the vehicle
brake failure warning light illuminated
need to downshift or use parking brakes to slow or stop the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Output Shaft and Transfer Case Mating Part Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission output shaft and transfer case mating part can cause the vehicle to refuse to move, leading to potential accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle refuses to move
rusted and stripped splines on the transmission output shaft and transfer case mating part
clean areas of the transmission and transfer case apart from the rust dislodged during disassembly.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Front Axle Separation and Front Differential Lockup
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The separation of the front axle from the front differential or the front differential lockup can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to potential accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle acts as if it went into neutral
grinding sound when trying to place the vehicle in park
the vehicle rolls backwards
front wheels lock up at high speeds
front tires will not turn and are completely locked up.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear axle can cause the vehicle to jerk violently, leading to potential accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks violently
rear axles are out of round
axles and drive shaft need to be replaced.
